# Runix Hub · Design Vision **0.3 “Nova”**  
*Turning every scientific claim into a runnable, fork-able, verifiable artefact.*

---

## 0 · The Three Pillars (North-star)  

| Emoji | Pillar                | What It Means in the UI |
|-------|-----------------------|-------------------------|
| 🗂️    | **Versioned Knowledge**   | Immutable Git-grade history for data, protocols, results |
| 🛠️    | **Composable Models & Tools** | Plug-and-play foundation models, simulators, workflows |
| 🤝    | **Human–AI Collaboration**   | Live agent suggestions, social review, lineage graphs |

> **Design rule:** every primary surface is tagged to one dominant pillar; use matching accent, icon & motion.

